Package: rjd3production
Title: Prepare for Production of Seasonal Adjustment with 'JDemetra+'
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tanguy", "Barthelemy", , "tanguy.barthelemy@insee.fr", role = c("aut", "cre", "art"))
Description: A comprehensive tool for setting up CVS-CJO data pipelines using 
  'JDemetra+' (version 3) and 'rjdverse'. This includes setting up a new working 
  environment, creating and selecting calendar regressors, managing 
  specifications (CJO and outliers) at the workspace level, making a workspace 
  crunchable, removing insignificant outliers, and comparing workspaces. 
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
